{"author":"Claude","data":{"alias":"dowdy-swear-bird","description":"# Agentic code-review capability for rebar (off by default, source-separated), dogfooded via the Gerrit LLM-Review gate\n\n## Context\nBuild the agentic code-review capability as a SEPARATE, OFF-BY-DEFAULT rebar capability whose source is clearly isolated so it has no effect when disabled. It uses the three-pass review structure (evidence -> binary-verify -> deterministic gate) and is enforced through Gerrit's `LLM-Review` label on the AWS-hosted environment. Dogfooding on rebar itself is the success criterion.\n\n## Success Criteria\n- Code review runs as the rebar MCP server's `LLM-Review` voter in Gerrit, off by default and source-isolated (inert and clearly non-applicable when the feature flag is off).\n- rebar's own changes are reviewed and gated by it end-to-end through the Gerrit gate (dogfood).\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] Capability is OFF by default (config/env gated) and SOURCE-SEPARATED into its own module(s), so the code path is inert and unmistakably non-applicable when disabled.\n- [ ] Uses the three-pass framework from the reviewer-migration epic (pass-1 evidence -> pass-2 verifier agent -> pass-3 deterministic typed gate).\n- [ ] Provider-agnostic via rebar's existing multi-provider runner; engine = native `review_code` (an optional PR-Agent runner may sit behind the runner seam but is not required).\n- [ ] Wired as the Gerrit `LLM-Review` voter: on patchset-created, review the change, run pass-1/2/3, and vote `LLM-Review` via REST; the deterministic block/advisory outcome maps to the label.\n- [ ] Hard auto-block reserved for high-precision categories (secrets / High-Critical security); everything else advisory at the starting (high) thresholds.\n- [ ] Dogfood proof: at least one real rebar change is reviewed + gated end-to-end on the AWS/Gerrit environment.","id":"b744-4fb9-2d05-4b49","parent_id":"","priority":1,"tags":["review","code-review","llm","gerrit"],"ticket_type":"epic","title":"Agentic code-review capability (off-by-default, source-separated); dogfood on rebar via Gerrit LLM-Review gate"},"env_id":"a7f6c5e0-d538-4904-841a-a3fd102c21d7","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1781990424759460536,"uuid":"fe52c405-9f58-41c2-b2d0-d138c73ac2e2"}